Ausroad’s newest Stemming Truck leaves home base, in Brisbane, Queensland bound for Rio Tinto’s Paraburdoo Mine in the Pilbara Region, Western Australia. Sam, who recently joined the Ausroad team (along with husband Greg), drove the Stemming Truck across the Country to Perth. The new Stemming Hire Truck (APS21)  joins an existing Stemming Hire Truck (APS16) at Rio Tinto’s Paraburdoo Site.  A third Stemming Hire Truck (APS08) is also currently on hire at Rio Tinto’s Hope Downs Iron Ore Mine Site , also situated in the Pilbara Region, Western Australia.